#app {

 to {

 }
}

[v-cloak]:before {
 content: "";
 box-sizing: border-box;
 position: absolute;
 top: 50%;
 left: 50%;
 width: 20px;
 height: 20px;
 margin-top: -10px;
 margin-left: -10px;
 border-radius: 50%;
 border: 2px solid #ccc;
 border-top-color: #333;
 animation: spinner 0.6s linear infinite;
 text-indent: 100%;

 overflow: hidden;
}

[v-cloak] > * {
 display: none;
}
